      "content": "it's just hard to see the point in \"carrying the weight.\" what's the point of carrying it if the weight is all there is? it honestly feels like i'm just an inconvenience to the world now, just taking up space in a house that's meant for two. everything i do feels so incredibly heavy and meaningless.",
